text: @FedExHelp hello, I was expecting a package today but received a “not at residence” tag on the gate. FedEx has my gate code. Can the delivery person be notified this on the next attempt?

@Crotin Hi, this is Fatimah  Thanks for reaching out.  I can look into that for you.  Please DM your name, address, city, state, zip code, tracking number, phone number, and email address. https://t.co/7vnSkvqx3r
